#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:517
msgid ""
"Prime Point was founded on a simple belief: the best way to build a strong "
"mind is through deliberate, structured practice. We connect passionate "
"learners with expert masters and give them the tools to grow — at their own "
"pace, on their own terms."
msgstr ""
"Prime Point oddiy bir e'tiqod asosida tashkil etilgan: kuchli ong qurishning "
"eng yaxshi yo'li — maqsadli, tizimli mashq. Biz ishtiyoqli o'quvchilarni "
"mutaxassis ustodlar bilan bog'laymiz va ularga o'sish uchun qurollar beramiz "
"— o'z sur'atlarida, o'z shartlarida."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:520
msgid ""
"We are not just a quiz app. We are a full learning ecosystem — from homework "
"assignments to live discussion, from beginner practices to expert-level "
"challenges."
msgstr ""
"Biz shunchaki viktorina ilovasi emasmiz. Biz to'liq ta'lim ekotizimizmiz — "
"uy vazifalaridan jonli muhokamagacha, boshlang'ich mashqlardan ekspert "
"darajasidagi qiyinchiliklargacha."

