#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:565
msgid ""
"Hundreds of curated practice sessions across subjects and difficulty levels. "
"Filter by topic, master, or level — and track your score every attempt."
msgstr ""
"Turli fanlar va qiyinlik darajalari bo'yicha yuzlab tanlangan mashq "
"sessiyalari. Mavzu, ustod yoki daraja bo'yicha filtrlang — va har bir "
"urinishda natijangizni kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:569 prime/templates/prime/help.html:588
msgid "Homework System"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:570
msgid ""
"Masters assign targeted practice as homework to individual students or "
"groups. Deadlines, auto-grading, and submission tracking built in."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga uy vazifasi sifatida maqsadli "
"mashqlar tayinlaydi. Muddatlar, avtomatik baholash va topshiriqlarni "
"kuzatish o'rnatilgan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:574
msgid "Master Profiles"
msgstr "Ustod profillari"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:575
msgid ""
"Follow experts in your field. Each master curates their own practice library "
"and can guide their students through structured learning paths."
msgstr ""
"Sohangizdagi mutaxassislarni kuzating. Har bir ustod o'zining mashqlar "
