#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:580
msgid ""
"Engage with the community — ask questions, share insights, vote on answers, "
"and learn from conversations that go beyond the practice sheet."
msgstr ""
"Jamoa bilan muloqot qiling — savollar bering, fikrlar ulashing, javoblarga "
