msgid "What Masters Can Do"
msgstr "Ustodlar nima qila oladi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:468
msgid ""
"Approved Masters have a full suite of teaching and management tools at their "
"disposal."
msgstr ""
"Tasdiqlangan Ustodlarda o'qitish va boshqarish uchun to'liq vositalar "
"to'plami mavjud."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:474
msgid "Create Practices"
msgstr "Mashqlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:475
msgid ""
"Build multiple-choice question sets with difficulty levels (easy / medium / "
"hard), time limits, pass scores, and max attempt caps."
msgstr ""
"Qiyinlik darajasi (oson / o'rta / qiyin), vaqt chegarasi, o'tish bali va "
"maksimal urinishlar bilan test savollari to'plamlari tuzing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:479
msgid "Manage Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilarni boshqarish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:480
msgid ""
"View everyone who follows you. Remove students from your roster and organise "
"them into named groups for bulk operations."
msgstr ""
"Sizi kuzatayotgan barcha kishilarni ko'ring. O'quvchilarni ro'yxatdan "
"o'chiring va ommaviy amallar uchun ularni nomlangan guruhlarga joylashtiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:484
msgid "Create Groups"
msgstr "Guruhlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:485
msgid ""
"Group students by class, level, or any criteria. Assign homework to a whole "
"group with a single action instead of individually."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilarni sinf, daraja yoki boshqa mezonlar bo'yicha guruhlang. Har biri "
"alohida o'rniga bitta amal bilan butun guruhga uy vazifasi tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:489
msgid "Assign Homework"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tayinlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:490
msgid ""
"Link any practice to individual students or groups, add notes, and set an "
"optional deadline. Track status — Pending, Submitted, or Graded."
msgstr ""
"Har qanday mashqni alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga bog'lang, izoh "
"qo'shing va ixtiyoriy muddat belgilang. Holat — Kutilmoqda, Topshirilgan "
"yoki Baholangan."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:494
msgid "Write Tutorials"
msgstr "Darsliklar yozish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:495
msgid ""
"Publish rich-text articles with a category, thumbnail, and linked practices. "
"Students can like or dislike your tutorials."
msgstr ""
"Kategoriya, eskiz va bog'langan mashqlar bilan boy matnli maqolalar chop "
"eting. O'quvchilar darsliklaringizni yoqtirishi yoki yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:499
msgid "Run Classrooms"
msgstr "Darsxonalarni yuritish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:500
msgid ""
"Create private classrooms with structured lessons. Attach practices, "
"homework, and tutorials to each lesson. Host a classroom-level discussion."
msgstr ""
"Tuzilgan darslar bilan xususiy darsxonalar yarating. Har bir darsga "
"mashqlar, uy vazifalari va darsliklarni biriktiring. Darsxona darajasida "
"muhokama o'tkazing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:504
msgid "Generate Certificates"
msgstr "Sertifikatlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:505
msgid ""
"Issue printable certificates to your students directly from your Master "
"profile page — no third-party tool needed."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilaringizga Ustod profili sahifangizdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri chop "
"etiladigan sertifikatlar bering — uchinchi tomon vositasi shart emas."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:512
msgid "For Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilar uchun"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:513
msgid "Student Guide"
msgstr "O'quvchi qo'llanmasi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:519
msgid "How to Choose and Follow a Master"
msgstr "Ustod qanday tanlanadi va obuna qilinadi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:520
msgid ""
"Browse the Masters list to see all approved educators. Click any master to "
"view their profile, subject, average student score, and the practices they "
"have published."
msgstr ""
"Barcha tasdiqlangan o'qituvchilarni ko'rish uchun Ustodlar ro'yxatiga "
"o'ting. Profilini, fanini, o'quvchilarning o'rtacha balini va chop etilgan "
"mashqlarini ko'rish uchun istalgan ustodga bosing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:522
msgid "Go to your Profile page after logging in."
msgstr "Kirganingizdan so'ng Profil sahifangizga o'ting."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:523
msgid ""
"Scroll to the Masters section and use the selector to add the masters you "
"want to follow."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar bo'limiga o'ting va kuzatmoqchi bo'lgan ustodlarni qo'shish uchun "
"tanlagichdan foydalaning."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:524
msgid ""
"Save your profile. The master's practices and homework will now be "
"accessible to you."
msgstr ""
"Profilingizni saqlang. Ustodning mashqlari va uy vazifalari endi sizga ochiq "
"bo'ladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:525
msgid "You can follow multiple masters at the same time."
msgstr "Bir vaqtning o'zida bir nechta ustodga obuna bo'lish mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:526
msgid "Remove a master from your selector at any time to unfollow."
msgstr ""
