msgstr "Platforma xususiyatlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:562
msgid "Practice System"
msgstr "Mashqlar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:563
msgid ""
"Practices are the core of Prime Point. Each practice is a set of multiple-"
"choice questions created by a master. Masters configure exactly how students "
"experience each practice."
msgstr ""
"Mashqlar Prime Pointning asosi. Har bir mashq ustod tomonidan yaratilgan "
"ko'p tanlovli savollar to'plami. Ustodlar o'quvchilar har bir mashqni qanday "
"boshdan kechirishini aniq sozlaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:565
msgid "Three difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, Hard."
msgstr "Uchta qiyinlik darajasi: Oson, O'rta, Qiyin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:566
msgid ""
"Optional time limit — the timer counts down and auto-submits when it expires."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy vaqt chegarasi — taymer orqaga hisoblaydi va muddati tugaganda "
"avtomatik topshiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:567
msgid "Pass score threshold — you must reach this percentage to pass."
msgstr "O'tish bali chegarasi — o'tish uchun ushbu foizga yetishingiz kerak."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:568
msgid ""
"Max attempts cap — masters can limit how many times a student can retry."
msgstr ""
"Maksimal urinishlar chegarasi — ustodlar o'quvchi necha marta qayta "
"urinishini cheklashi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:569
msgid ""
"Show-answers-after option — correct answers are revealed once the attempt is "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ri javoblarni ko'rsatish opsiyasi — urinish tugagandan so'ng to'g'ri "
"javoblar ochiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:570
msgid ""
"Free and available-for-all flags — masters can open a practice to the entire "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Bepul va hammaga ochiq bayroqlar — ustodlar mashqni butun platforma uchun "
"ochaoladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:575
msgid "Practice Metadata"
msgstr "Mashq ma'lumotlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:576
msgid "Level"
msgstr "Daraja"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:577 prime/templates/prime/help.html:633
#: tutorial/templates/tutorial/tutorial_detail.html:99
msgid "min"
msgstr "daqiqa"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:579
msgid "Max Attempts"
msgstr "Maks. urinishlar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:589
msgid ""
"Masters link a practice to a homework assignment and push it directly to "
"students or groups. Students complete the linked practice to submit the "
"homework."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar mashqni uy vazifasiga bog'laydi va to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'quvchilarga "
"yoki guruhlarga yuboradi. O'quvchilar uy vazifasini topshirish uchun "
"bog'langan mashqni bajaradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:591
msgid ""
"Create homework: give it a title, optional notes, a linked practice, and an "
"optional due date."
msgstr ""
"Uy vazifasini yarating: sarlavha, ixtiyoriy izoh, bog'langan mashq va "
"ixtiyoriy topshirish muddatini kiriting."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:592
msgid "Assign to individual students or to an entire group in one step."
msgstr "Bir qadamda alohida o'quvchilarga yoki butun guruhga tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:593
msgid ""
"Student completes the practice → homework status moves to Submitted "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchi mashqni bajaradi → uy vazifasi holati avtomatik ravishda "
"Topshirilgan'ga o'tadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:594
msgid "Master grades the submission and can leave written feedback."
msgstr "Ustod topshiriqni baholaydi va yozma fikr bildirishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:595
msgid "Track per-student status from the homework detail view."
msgstr ""
"Uy vazifasi tafsilotlari ko'rinishidan har bir o'quvchi holatini kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:607
msgid "Assignment Overview"
msgstr "Topshiriq ko'rinishi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:608
msgid "Group: Advanced Class"
msgstr "Guruh: Ilg'or sinf"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:608
msgid "students"
msgstr "o'quvchi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:609
msgid "Practice: Grammar Test 3"
msgstr "Mashq: Grammatika testi 3"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:610
msgid "Due date"
msgstr "Topshirish muddati"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:619
msgid "Tutorial System"
msgstr "Darsliklar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:620
msgid ""
"Tutorials are long-form rich-text articles written by masters. They can "
"include images, formatted text, and links to related practices — turning a "
"lesson into an interactive experience."
msgstr ""
"Darsliklar — ustodlar tomonidan yozilgan boy matnli uzun maqolalar. Ular "
"rasmlar, formatlangan matn va tegishli mashqlarga havolalarni o'z ichiga "
"olishi mumkin — darsni interaktiv tajribaga aylantiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:622
msgid "Categories: Mathematics, Korean, Programming, English, Other."
msgstr "Kategoriyalar: Matematika, Koreys, Dasturlash, Ingliz, Boshqa."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:623
msgid "Read time is estimated automatically from the word count."
msgstr "O'qish vaqti so'zlar sonidan avtomatik hisoblanadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:624
msgid "Students can like or dislike a tutorial to give the author feedback."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilar muallifga fikr bildirish uchun darslikni yoqtirishi yoki "
"yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:625
msgid ""
"Link any number of practices to a tutorial so students can test themselves "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilar darhol o'zlarini sinab ko'rishi uchun darslikka istalgan "
"miqdordagi mashqlarni bog'lang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:626
msgid ""
"View count is tracked so masters can see which tutorials are most popular."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rishlar soni kuzatiladi, shuning uchun ustodlar qaysi darsliklar "
"mashhurligini ko'rishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:631
msgid "Tutorial Card"
msgstr "Darslik kartasi"

