#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:646
msgid "Classroom System"
msgstr "Darsxona tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:647
msgid ""
"Classrooms are private learning spaces managed by a master. They contain "
"structured lessons, and only enrolled students can access the content."
msgstr ""
"Darsxonalar — ustod tomonidan boshqariladigan xususiy ta'lim makonlari. Ular "
"tuzilgan darslarni o'z ichiga oladi va faqat ro'yxatdan o'tgan o'quvchilar "
"kontentga kira oladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:649
msgid "Add students individually or import a whole group at once."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilarni alohida qo'shing yoki butun guruhni bir vaqtda import qiling."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:650
msgid ""
"Each classroom has ordered lessons with a status: Not Started, Ongoing, or "
"Finished."
msgstr ""
"Har bir darsxonada tartibli darslar mavjud: Boshlanmagan, Davom etmoqda yoki "
"Tugallangan."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:651
msgid "Attach practices, homework assignments, and tutorials to any lesson."
msgstr "Har qanday darsga mashqlar, uy vazifalari va darsliklarni biriktiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:652
msgid ""
"Upload lesson notes (PDFs, slides) that students can download per lesson."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilar har bir dars uchun yuklab olishi mumkin bo'lgan dars "
"eslatmalarini (PDF, slaydlar) yuklang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:653
msgid ""
"Each classroom has its own discussion board for class-specific questions."
msgstr ""
"Har bir darsxonada sinf-xususiy savollar uchun o'zining muhokama doskasi "
"mavjud."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:658
msgid "Lesson Structure"
msgstr "Dars tuzilishi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:661
