msgstr "Boshlanmagan"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:682
msgid ""
"The platform-wide discussion forum lets anyone ask questions, share "
"insights, or start a conversation. The best answers rise to the top through "
"community voting."
msgstr ""
"Platformadagi muhokama forumi har kimga savol berish, fikr ulashish yoki "
"suhbat boshlash imkonini beradi. Eng yaxshi javoblar jamoat ovoz berishi "
"orqali yuqoriga ko'tariladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:684
msgid "Threads are organised by category — find the right section quickly."
msgstr ""
"Mavzular kategoriya bo'yicha tartiblanadi — kerakli bo'limni tez toping."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:685
msgid "Announcements and pinned threads stay at the top of their category."
msgstr ""
"E'lonlar va mahkamlangan mavzular o'z kategoriyasining yuqorisida qoladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:686
msgid "Upvote helpful threads and replies — downvote off-topic ones."
msgstr ""
"Foydali mavzular va javoblarga ovoz bering — mavzuga mos kelmaydiganlarga "
"salbiy ovoz bering."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:687
msgid "Thread authors can mark one reply as the accepted answer."
msgstr ""
"Mavzu mualliflari bitta javobni qabul qilingan javob sifatida belgilashi "
"mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:688
msgid "Sort by Latest, Most Votes, Recent Activity, or Unanswered."
msgstr ""
"Eng yangi, Ko'p ovozli, So'nggi faollik yoki Javobsiz bo'yicha tartiblash."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:693
