#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:748
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Ko'p so'raladigan savollar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:758
msgid "Is Prime Point free?"
msgstr "Prime Point bepulmi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:763
msgid ""
"Yes. Creating an account, following masters, taking practices, and "
"participating in discussions is completely free. Some practices may be "
"marked as free by the master; others may be restricted to enrolled students "
"only."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Hisob yaratish, ustodlarga obuna bo'lish, mashqlar topshirish va "
"muhokamada ishtirok etish mutlaqo bepul. Ba'zi mashqlar ustod tomonidan "
"bepul deb belgilanishi mumkin; boshqalari faqat ro'yxatdan o'tgan "
"o'quvchilar uchun cheklanishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:773
msgid "How do I become a Master?"
msgstr "Qanday qilib Ustod bo'laman?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:778
msgid ""
"Visit the Masters page and click 'Become a Master'. Complete the short "
"application form with your name, subject area, and a brief description. An "
"administrator will review and approve your application. Once approved, all "
"master tools are unlocked immediately."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar sahifasiga o'ting va 'Ustod bo'lish' tugmasini bosing. Ismingiz, "
"fan sohaniz va qisqa tavsif bilan qisqa ariza shaklini to'ldiring. "
"Administrator arizangizni ko'rib chiqadi va tasdiqlaydi. Tasdiqlanganidan "
"so'ng barcha ustod vositalari darhol ochiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:788
msgid "How do I follow a Master?"
msgstr "Ustodga qanday obuna bo'laman?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:793
msgid ""
"Go to your Profile page and scroll to the Masters section. Use the multi-"
"select to add any masters you want to follow, then save your profile. You "
"can add or remove masters at any time the same way."
msgstr ""
"Profil sahifangizga o'ting va Ustodlar bo'limiga o'ting. Kuzatmoqchi bo'lgan "
"ustodlarni qo'shish uchun ko'p tanlovdan foydalaning, so'ng profilingizni "
"saqlang. Xuddi shu tarzda istalgan vaqt ustodlarni qo'shish yoki o'chirish "
"mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:803
msgid "How are points earned?"
msgstr "Ballar qanday to'planadi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:808
msgid ""
"Each time you complete a practice, points are added to your student profile "
"based on your score. Higher scores give more points. Points accumulate "
"across all practices and determine your rank on the platform."
msgstr ""
"Har safar mashqni bajarganingizda, ballaringizga qarab o'quvchi "
"profilingizga ball qo'shiladi. Yuqori ball ko'proq ball beradi. Ballar "
"barcha mashqlar bo'yicha to'planadi va platformadagi darajangizni belgilaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:818
msgid "What happens if I exceed the maximum attempts on a practice?"
msgstr "Mashqdagi maksimal urinishlardan oshib ketsam nima bo'ladi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:823
msgid ""
"Once you reach the maximum attempts set by the master, the Start button is "
"disabled and you will see a message indicating you have used all your "
"attempts. Contact your master if you need an additional attempt."
msgstr ""
"Ustod tomonidan belgilangan maksimal urinishlarga yetganingizdan so'ng, "
"Boshlash tugmasi o'chiriladi va barcha urinishlaringizni ishlatganligi "
"haqida xabar ko'rasiz. Qo'shimcha urinish kerak bo'lsa, ustodingizga "
"murojaat qiling."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:833
msgid "Can I enroll in multiple classrooms?"
msgstr "Bir nechta darsxonaga yozilish mumkinmi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:838
msgid ""
"Yes. A master can add you to as many classrooms as they manage. Each "
"classroom is independent with its own lessons, content, and discussion board."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Ustod sizni boshqaradigan darsxonalarning istalganiga qo'shishi mumkin. "
"Har bir darsxona o'z darslari, kontenti va muhokama doskasi bilan mustaqil."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:848
msgid "Can a master see my homework submissions and scores?"
msgstr "Ustod uy vazifasini topshirishlarimni va ballarimni ko'ra oladimi?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:853
msgid ""
"Yes. When a master assigns homework, they can view each student's submission "
"status, score, and any written feedback they leave. This lets masters track "
"progress and provide personalised guidance."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Ustod uy vazifasini tayinlaganida, har bir o'quvchining topshirish "
"holati, bali va qoldirgan yozma fikrlarini ko'rishi mumkin. Bu ustodlarga "
"rivojlanishni kuzatish va shaxsiylashtirilgan yo'riqnoma berish imkonini "
"beradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:863
msgid "What tutorial categories are available?"
msgstr "Qanday darslik kategoriyalari mavjud?"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:868
msgid ""
"Tutorials are organised into five categories: Mathematics, Korean, "
"Programming, English, and Other. Masters choose the best matching category "
"when publishing a tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Darsliklar beshta kategoriyaga bo'lingan: Matematika, Koreys, Dasturlash, "
"Ingliz va Boshqa. Ustodlar darslik chop etishda eng mos kategoriyani "
"tanlaydi."

